sentences.sentence: There exist wide tidal fiats in Qiantang Estuary.
sentences.translation: 钱塘江河口存在广阔的潮滩地。

sentences.sentence: As Adam Jonas of Morgan Stanley points out, there is no certainty that American customers will flock to buy rebadged small Fiats.
sentences.translation: 如摩根·士丹利的亚当琼纳斯所指出，还无法确定美国消费者是否会蜂拥地去买换了商标的小型菲亚特车。
